hopobject.body: I'm a partner in hawaiipacifichealth.jobs Chrissy Teigen may have few qualms about baring it all in a swimsuit, but we're betting the Sports Illustrated model probably wishes she had covered up a tad more during a day out in New York City. The brunette beauty's sheer shirt slipped to reveal more than she bargained for during a shopping trip in the Big Apple on Sept. 30, 2013. At least she looks like she can laugh it off!
